<div id="banner">
	<h1>Evidence</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p>Godfrey Reggio: <a href="http://www.koyaanisqatsi.org/films/evidence.php">Evidence: The pervasive nature of Technology</a>.  This looks very interesting, anyone know where I can get a copy? It&#8217;s only eight minutes, so maybe it&#8217;s available somewhere on the Internet.</p>

<p><a href="http://www.koyaanisqatsi.org/films/godfrey.php">Reggio</a> is the director behind the <a href="http://www.koyaanisqatsi.org/films/film.php">Qatsi Trilogy</a>, &#8220;essays of visual images and sound which chronicle the destructive impact of the modern world on the environment.&#8221; They&#8217;re wonderful, go down to your library or video store and get them today.</p>

<p class="posted">posted March 21, 2002 08:07 PM (<a class="category" href="http://www.aaronsw.com/weblog/cat_education">Education</a>)  <a href="000197" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

